Read the developer documentation entry file at **docs/README.md**. It lists all project guidelines and when to read each doc (always-applied vs by-topic). Follow the entry file's instructions: load the docs it marks as always apply, and load any doc it lists under "Read when relevant" when your task touches that topic.

